{"tid":96453,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後竟然想農曆前夕準時走？洗唔洗俾你放半日添呀！","createTime":"2017-01-27T00:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:39:19.000Z","uid":19334,"like":9,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7810890d5d8b071804fb731376b70ca1a01ec7d7","tid":96453,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"係人都會知嚟緊係農曆新年，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁好多公司都會早放，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁當然唔包括我公司啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我係外國企業，所以唔包埋都好正常，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知有隻90後，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢今年啱啱先入職，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就問我公司會唔會有早放，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我叫佢用下個腦自己都諗，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就講果日約左屋企人食團年飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n六點鬆會走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就即刻鬧到佢差d cry，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲串爆佢咁問佢洗唔洗放埋羅馬歷，儒略曆比你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後真係好貪小便宜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早走果一陣都想貪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d33a11df81c7796f661fa12288b59d32d010691","tid":96453,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:45:50.000Z","msg":"放你 3 點走唔通你 3 點返屋企食團年飯咩<br />\n呃撚到人咩 90 後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a687690bfe8660b723f1c8fc477ae043e43b51f5","tid":96453