 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢今年啱啱先入職，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就問我公司會唔會有早放，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我叫佢用下個腦自己都諗，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就講果日約左屋企人食團年飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n六點鬆會走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就即刻鬧到佢差d cry，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲串爆佢咁問佢洗唔洗放埋羅馬歷，儒略曆比你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後真係好貪小便宜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早走果一陣都想貪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢問有咩問題<br />\n你習慣係你嘅事<br />\n自己想放泄就咪咁多借口啦柒頭"},{"pid":"64219f7b2ae30774466e78e5628808c1df4bbda1","tid":96453,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"今晚我特登做通宵搏表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db74e7aad82d9f34f8afe3ecca1ba4477e5576c","tid":96453,"uid":73612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"間間公司都有唔同規矩㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n問清楚到底有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7c981a1a08b0e4a58a95a52f0d4f6e5ff9e03b","tid":96453,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚我特登做通宵搏表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好有心<br />\n<br />\n實加分"},{"pid":"401354a27a9a3447db583c1d70825c63c1dfca52","tid":96453,"uid":60365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今晚我特登做通宵搏表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma